author: William Blake
message: In seed time learn, in harvest teach, in winter enjoy.

author: Cheng Yen
message: Happiness does not come from having much, but from being attached to little.

author: Richard Bach
message: Every gift from a friend is a wish for your happiness.

author: Ralph Emerson
message: Go put your creed into the deed. Nor speak with double tongue.
